text: (──...Looks like you're struggling with all those bags...)
Chiyoko, do you want me to carry something?

Eh? Oh, thank you so much!
But I'm okay, it's not heavy or anything──!
Sorry for taking up so much space...!

Oh no, it's really nothing.
As long as you're not having a hard time, Chiyoko──

I might have gone overboard with the snacks,
getting a bit too excited.

Yes! I thought the training camp would be tough,
so it might be fun for everyone to have a treat during free time.
...Well, I also wanted to eat them...!

─Ah! Of course, I also chose some that are good for recovery
and some low-sugar, high-protein ones, you know!?

...Some of them are just regular ones...!
I just wanted everyone to enjoy them!

You're not doing anything wrong, so don't worry about it.
I hope everyone will be happy.
